da</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents.html\">Sponsor your parents and grandparents</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<nav class=\"provisional gc-subway\">\n<h1 id=\"gc-document-nav\">Sponsor your parents and grandparents</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/undertaking.html\">What it means to be a sponsor</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/undertaking.html#gc-document-nav\">What it means to be a sponsor</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/eligibility.html\">Check if you’re eligible</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/eligibility.html#gc-document-nav\">Check if you’re eligible</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/who-you-can-sponsor.html\">Who you can sponsor</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/who-you-can-sponsor.html#gc-document-nav\">Who you can sponsor</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/tell-us-you-want-sponsor-parent-grandparent.html\">Submit your interest to sponsor form</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/tell-us-you-want-sponsor-parent-grandparent.html#gc-document-nav\">Submit your interest to sponsor form</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"active\" href=\"#\">Find out if you’re invited to apply</a> </li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/apply.html\">How to apply</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/apply.html#gc-document-nav\">How to apply</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/after-apply-next-steps.html\">After you apply</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/after-apply-next-steps.html#gc-document-nav\">After you apply</a>\n</li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/prepare-arrival.html\">Prepare for arrival</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/prepare-arrival.html#gc-document-nav\">Prepare for arrival</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n<h1 class=\"gc-thickline\" id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">Find out if you’re invited to apply</h1>\n<h2>2025 intake</h2>\n<p>Starting July 28, 2025, we invited potential sponsors who submitted an interest to sponsor form in 2020 to apply for the 2025 intake.</p>\n<p>We sent 17,860 invitations over approximately 2 weeks. Our goal is to accept 10,000 complete applications.</p>\n<p><strong>The last day to apply was October 9, 2025.</strong> We’re no longer accepting applications.</p>\n<h2>If you were invited to apply</h2>\n<p>We sent your invitation to the email address you put on your 2020 interest to sponsor form.</p>\n<!--\n<h3>Check your invitation status</h3>\n<p>Use the <a href=\"#check-invitation-status\">Check your invitation status tool</a> below to look up your confirmation number and see if you’ve been invited to apply.</p>\n<details>\n  <summary>If the tool says you’ve been invited but you didn’t get an invitation</summary>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Check your junk mail or spam folder to make sure you didn’t miss the email.</li>\n    <li>If we couldn’t send you the invitation by email, we sent it by mail to the mailing address you put on your 2020 interest to sponsor form. Check your physical mailbox.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>If you still can’t find your invitation, use the <a href=\"https://secure.cic.gc.ca/SponsorPGPParrainerPGP/en/Home\">Find your lost confirmation number page</a> to ask for a copy.</p>\n</details>\n<details>\n  <summary>If your email address has changed or you’ve lost your confirmation number</summary>\n  <p>Use the <a href=\"https://secure.cic.gc.ca/SponsorPGPParrainerPGP/en/Home\">Find your lost confirmation number page</a> to</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>get your confirmation number</li>\n    <li>get a copy of your invitation to apply, if you’ve been invited</li>\n    <li>tell us your new email address if you’ve changed it</li>\n  </ul>\n</details>\n<div id=\"check-invitation-status\" class='hidden mrgn-tp-xl'>\n  <div class='wb-fieldflow' data-wb-fieldflow='{\n        \"live\": true,\n\t\t\"hideelm\": \"#pe\",\n\t\t\"unhideelm\": \"#check-invitation-status\"\n   }'>\n    <div class='wb-fieldflow-header'>\n      <p class='wb-fieldflow-label'>What does your confirmation number start with?</p>\n      <p>See <a class='wb-lbx' href='#conf_num'>where to find your confirmation number</a>.</p>\n    </div>\n    <ul>\n      <li>A\n        <div class='wb-fieldflow-sub'>\n          <p>What’s the second character?</p>\n          <ul>\n            <li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"ajax\", \"url\": \"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/selected/a1.html#a1\", \"container\": \"#table\", \"clean\": \"#table\"}'>Number</li>\n            <li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"ajax\", \"url\": \"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/selected/aa.html#aa\", \"container\": \"#table\", \"clean\": \"#table\"}'>Letter</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </li>\n      <li>B\n        <div class='wb-fieldflow-sub'>\n          <p>What’s the second character?</p>\n          <ul>\n            <li data-wb-fieldflow='{ \"action\": \"ajax\", \"url\": \"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/selected/b1.html#b1\", \"container\": \"#table\", \"clean\": \"#table\"}'>Number</li>\n            <li data-wb-fieldflow='{ \"action\": \"ajax\", \"url\": \"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/selected/ba.html#ba\", \"container\": \"#table\", \"clean\": \"#table\"}'>Letter</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </li>\n      <li>C\n        <div class='wb-fieldflow-sub'>\n          <p>What’s the second character?</p>\n          <ul>\n            <li data-wb-fieldflow='{ \"action\": \"ajax\", \"url\": \"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/selected/c1.html#c1\", \"container\": \"#table\", \"clean\": \"#table\"}'>Number</li>\n            <li data-wb-fieldflow='{ \"action\": \"ajax\", \"url\": \"/content/canadasite